{"tid":1942702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(免費的才是最貴) 保誠推免費保障確診武漢肺炎賠$10000","createTime":"2020-03-25T08:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T08:55:39.000Z","uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"274571e92450098b5684cefe8112a881a557af68","tid":1942702,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"*保障概要*<br />\n．確診賠償HK$10,000<br />\n．身故賠償 HK$100,000<br />\n．所有18歲以下的子女同時受保<br />\n<br />\n*登記詳情*<br />\n✅登記日期: 即日起至2020年4月24日<br />\n✅合資格人士: 18歲或以上香港身份證持有人<br />\n✅保障期: 45天<br />\n✅名額: 300,000先到先得 <br />\n<br />\n*如何登記?*<br />\n1. 下載Pulse by Prudential及登記帳戶 (須以香港流動電話號碼登記) <a href=\"https://pruhk.app.link/pulse_covid19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpruhk.app.link%2Fpulse_covid19&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=7565eb84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pruhk.app.link/pulse_covid19</a><br />\n2. 進入免費保障專頁及完成登記<br />\n3. 確認電郵連同保障條款將於24小時內收到<br />\n<br />\n更多詳情，請登入<br />\n<a href=\"http://prudential.com.hk/covid-ws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprudential.com.hk%2Fcovid-ws&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=b3173776\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">prudential.com.hk/covid-ws</a>"},{"pid":"ae840cd36edb3df772345e6c72a6abbaac4a467d","tid":1942702,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:50:24.000Z","msg":"好撚賤, 聽講就算你揀左唔要接受推廣, 你個電話都會比左aa狗做warm call<br />\n希望香港有大爆發, 爆到保誠執笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772ed2c258deb2fc9db61ef4bcb432e82135bdf1","tid":1942702,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:54:37.000Z","msg":"保費都唔止1萬"},{"pid":"3e5e8aa77f67101d37e039a66b55e7ee0f80f82f","tid":1942702,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:55:21.000Z","msg":"既然免費<br />\n咁點解唔由宜家開始 揀頭35個確診者 派錢？<br />\n其實佢都知區區35人 其實好難中招 最多咪幾個"},{"pid":"1cd059191205